Package org.knime.core.eclipseUtil

Contains only utility classes needed to make Eclipse work together with the KNIME framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GlobalClassCreator Deprecated
    Since 2.4 the KNIME core is using the Eclipse Buddy-Classloading mechanism.
    GlobalObjectInputStream
    ObjectInputStream which uses the GlobalClassCreator to resolve Objects by class name.
    OSGIHelper
    This class contains some methods to access OSGI information that may not be available if the program is not running in a complete OSGI framework.
    UpdateChecker
    Checks for updates to new feature releases.
    UpdateChecker.UpdateInfo
    Information about an available update.

Package org.knime.core.eclipseUtil Description

Contains only utility classes needed to make Eclipse work together with the KNIME framework.

Further details relating to this eclipse feature are available in the eclipse bug database, #85116, and in the knime bug database, #73.
